 44	 *   - `boundary-discipline`: the document crosses the boundary exactly once —
 45	 *     `Schema`-decoded on read — and is converted HERE to the legacy
 46	 *     route/component shape (per-locale strings, `[start, end]` millisecond
 47	 *     tuples, leading-`/` image URLs) so component code is UNCHANGED.
 48	 *   - `use-the-platform`: the read cache is Effect's built-in
 49	 *     `Effect.cachedInvalidateWithTTL` — it single-flights concurrent
