290	/**
291	 * The bucket key the *unpublished* draft lives at. The `/admin` editor (C5)
292	 * writes here on "Save draft" and reads here first so an in-progress edit
293	 * survives a reload without going live; "Publish" promotes the draft to
294	 * `SITE_CONTENT_KEY` and removes it. The public read path
295	 * (`getSiteContent`) never reads the draft.
296	 */
